cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS 

The paper proposes a novel approach to nonlinear manifold learning using optimization techniques, which is a common topic in machine learning and optimization research (cs.LG). The proposed algorithm is formulated as an instance of General Pattern Search (GPS) framework, which is a well-known optimization method (cs.NA). The paper also evaluates the proposed algorithm on synthetic and real datasets, which involves computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data science (cs.DS) techniques.
